Hi All, 

Lakshya just asked me to post this for W186:

Hi everyone!

Josh Hug is going to teach CS W186 next semester, and we're looking for qualified TAs to fill the boots of the 6 people we're losing from staff.

If you're interested, please apply via the ASE form and then fill out this auxiliary form here https://forms.gle/nS65DvK8pRgbqnrF8. We'll try to hold some interviews over the next two weeks for it.

People taking the course this semester are also welcome to apply!

If you have any questions, just email Lakshya Jain.
